Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Nationwide Kojima-san Competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're taking part?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, your dad is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like he got in through a fish shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fish shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He meant "form screening."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They determine the participants by screening their\Napplication forms with their pictures and profiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dad must've been chosen because he's the greatest man!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never met him, but does that really sound like Genta's dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of prize does he get if he wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The letter that was sent mentioned a cash prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The amount was a one with seven zeroes behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seven zeroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's ten million yen, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, who organized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:00:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Orphanize?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Organize! I mean, who sent that letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was sent from Nichiuri TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But instead of the money, my dad seems\Nto want the boar scroll bonus prize more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was really sent by Nichiuri TV, it shouldn't be a scam, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bonus prize is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, there's a boar drawn on the scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when I saw the photo in the letter,\Nit was a black and white painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I thought it wasn't a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dad is a big fan of boars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted to hang it in the alcove.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also said the painter's name sounded\Nlike "Thank You," so he loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Thank You"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, maybe it's the money that's considered a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ten million yen is just a bonus?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is magic, attack the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On Saturday nights, be sure to click on Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:01:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta's dad is one of the suspects and is in a huge pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's worth fifty million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This scroll is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if it was really made by the legendary\Nink-and-wash painter - Sankyuu Shounin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I've seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dad said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's called "bush, clover, and boar."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's one of the patterns on the flower cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would a replica of the flower card be worth so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When people first found out about this painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sankyuu claimed it was only a random doodling, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They then found two more scrolls by Sankyuu\Nwith the deer and the butterfly on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Causing their value to skyrocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together, you get "boar-deer-butterfly,"\Nwhich is considered good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, there was once a young entrepreneur who\Nbought those with all of his pocket money...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He ended up raking in huge profits and success,\Nwhich added to the value of the scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it really is a scroll that brings luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since one of the scrolls is the prize, does\Nthat mean he sold it? That entrepreneur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, if he had sold it then the media would have covered it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I think he still has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, what was that entrepreneur's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kojima Gonsaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the president of the Kojima Group, and\Nthe sponsor of this Kojima-san Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kojima Group"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the rich guy who owns all\Nthose railways and department stores?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since he lost two of the three scrolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said the last one is useless to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And has decided to give it away as a prize in this competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he wrote on his blog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted it to go to another Kojima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's lucky you're a Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, was that letter sent directly to your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was sent to another nearby Kojima's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the blog said anyone named Kojima could enter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They asked my dad if he was interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will they have to do in order to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strength test...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A singing contest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a kanji writing test, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They want a Kojima-san who's strong in every aspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my dad's singing is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even better than Conan over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that setting the bar too low?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will Genta-kun's dad be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, whoever gets the highest total points\Nbetween the three tests wins, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, there's more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those who pass the three tests report to the 5th studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll determine the winner in front of us spectators.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a trivia game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, all five machines checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they'll just play a trivia game in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so those are the Kojima-san's who are participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was the competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The test was to do as many push-ups as you could in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave it my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did over 180 and still got eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, whoever passes this must be a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun's dad is going to be all right, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll easily win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like more Kojima-san's are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd get eliminated in the singing round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well, it just can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even this guy who's won consecutive singing awards got eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like you needed the voice of Presley to pass this round.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By Presley, did he mean the kung fu movie actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Bruce Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're referring to the king of Rock 'n' Roll, Elvis Presley.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will he be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun's dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why!? Why me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's another group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I aced the Level 1 Kanji Aptitude Test, so\Nhow is it possible that I got eliminated?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My answers were all perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they weren't totally perfect...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, could you write these?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you write the kanji for "rose" and "melancholy"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey; Genta, your dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's from dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one of the three finalists?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's cheering for you, so be sure to nail this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are five seats for the finalists...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did they only pick three?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President Kojima...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The TV network producer is complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said we can't do a show this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't mind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}In any case, did you show it to those three finalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:54.86,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H5A2643&\blur1\be5\fad(210,0)}Kojima Gonsaku (71)\N{\fs13}Kojima Group President
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:10:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm asking if you've shown them the piece of paper I prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all three of them responded to it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just tell me how they pronounced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Number 35, Kojima Bunta-san answered "happyakuichi" - 801.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:19.34,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(210,0)}Kojima Bunta (33)\NParticipant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Number 84, Kojima Genji-san answered "shakuhachi" - bamboo flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:24.56,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(210,0)}Kojima Genji (32)\NParticipant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Number 147, Kojima Gankichi-san answered "ippin" - first class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:29.81,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(250,0)}Kojima Gankichi (34)\NParticipant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's exposed his tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using money to draw him out was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's that piece of paper now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll handle things from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, president...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall go to his waiting room and extend\Nmy welcome to this man personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the winner of the Kojima-san Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dad should be showing up at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a Nichiuri TV staff member.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for any inconvenience...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But due to a problem on our side, the Kojima-san Competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is officially cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That smudge on his sleeve...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A blood stain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President Kojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you call an ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be here in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he missed a step and fell down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just heard a scream and a loud sound, so I rushed here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:21.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I saw the president lying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should call the police, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look here, at the president's right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's holding a torn piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, if someone lost their footing\Nand was about to fall down the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't hold onto a piece of paper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:42.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either the president grabbed the paper out\Nof someone's hand as he was falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or he was fighting with someone over the paper, causing the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the staff member who went on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw blood on his sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was with us when we ran here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:13:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He tried to straighten the president up, so\Nperhaps that's when blood got on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, there was someone near the president when he fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by the time you got here, they vanished with the rest of the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that someone is responsible for his fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, that someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is among the three people who passed the preliminary rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would extend his welcome to the champion personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the staff was waiting in another room for his return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, don't tell me those three finalists...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what's all this racket about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you hurry and start the trivia game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta's dad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, besides that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one of these three is Genta's dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our victim is Kojima Gonsaku-san, age 71.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the president of the Kojima Group...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he's here today as the head judge\Nof a special program for Nichiuri TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Head judge?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a show called "The Nationwide Kojima-san Competition,"\Nplanned and sponsored by President Kojima himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The winner is set to receive expensive prizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, it looks as if he slipped down the\Nstairs, making this an accidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:15:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem to be a case for us criminal investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you call us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you who called me directly, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we staff members rushed here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president was bleeding from his head and\Nholding a piece of paper while lying on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, when someone falls down the\Nstairs, they don't hold onto paper, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's possible that someone else was nearby,\Nand he grabbed the paper as he fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or he was fighting with someone over\Nthe paper and fell as a result, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we found the president lying on\Nthe floor, nobody else was around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which would mean someone left the president\Nhere, snatched the rest of the paper and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, this could be manslaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To observe all of this and contact us in the first division.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was that boy who wanted us to contact\NDetective Takagi from the police department.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the president's secretary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was told by the president not to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't know what was written on that piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was kept in an envelope, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that piece of paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the one the president was holding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That paper was only used by the president on\Nspecial occasions - a unique type called "washi."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it when the president put it in the envelope...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he only gave it to me for safekeeping for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And before leaving, I returned it to him with the envelope intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found an empty envelope on the\Nvictim's body, so that's likely the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did he let you keep it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He asked me to show it to those three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ones who passed the Kojima-san Competition preliminary rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kojima-san Competition, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, how did you select the participants?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We called for everyone with the\Nsurname of Kojima on the internet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And chose 200 people from the\Napplicants to participate in the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It consists of three-minutes of push ups for our physical test...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Singing a favorite song for our singing contest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a kanji writing quiz for our knowledge test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the ones who aced the knowledge, physical,\Nand singing tests are those three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More or less?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the president showed them the question on the piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He only asked me to listen to how they read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all three responses were all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All over the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it written as a code or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, all three answered immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I don't think it was a complicated word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Number 35, Kojima Bunta-san answered "happyakuichi" - 801.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Number 81, Kojima Genji-san answered "shakuhachi" - bamboo flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And number 147, Kojima Gankichi-san answered "ippin" - first class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three answers really were all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you really show them the same piece of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I reported their answers to the president, he muttered...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he exposed his tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right after that, he took the envelope from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And said he'd go to the waiting room himself to welcome the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The winner of the Kojima-san Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he decided the winner after hearing the three answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, it's odd to say something about a "tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he went to the winner's waiting room?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was told to leave, so I waited\Nin the staff room the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I heard the president scream, and a loud noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:42.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked the other people who participated in this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The waiting rooms for the finalists\Nare at the top of this flight of stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time of the president's fall, only\Nthose three finalists were on that floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were those three in the same room?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, they were in three separate rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the elevator to this floor is under maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stairs have to be used to go up or down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, when the staff rushed\Nhere under these circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there was no one around the president, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone among them must have pushed him\Ndown the stairs and returned to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the likely situation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, we should question them one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While you're questioning them, please\Nask a few extra questions for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's quite rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Usually you would just secretly follow us\Nand suddenly interrupt with questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun's dad is among those three?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never met him before, so I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:21:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might know me from photos or somewhere, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's like that, we can just ask and find out quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell Inspector Megure about it\Nand remove him from the suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holmes once said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to allow your judgment to be biased by personal qualities,\Nand emotional qualities are antagonistic to clear reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because he's Genta's dad doesn't mean\Nwe're 100% sure he's not the culprit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we want to conduct a proper investigation, it's best that we don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, can you help me ask the questions I'm about to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps those three...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't really ace those tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun still hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess something really did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard sirens from an ambulance and police cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we go and check out the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:21:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't Edogawa-kun tell us to stay here and wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this is really a criminal case, Genta-kun's\Nfather might be dragged into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this didn't involve him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:22.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd have called us and told us not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he still hasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The possibility of him being a suspect is very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kojima-kun's father, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.57,0:23:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hyakki Yakou...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That robber group?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.53,0:24:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I have to go take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.53,0:24:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.96,0:24:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyoite
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.94,0:24:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My dad is the greatest man, so he can't be the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.35,0:24:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That reasoning is flawed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.76,0:24:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.94,0:24:36.31,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Look forward to the next episode
